    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Park Avenue",
    "description": "If you're a passionate SEO Specialist with drive and ambition, Park Avenue in Noida is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Park Avenue:\nPark Avenue is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Park Avenue!",
